OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FItalian minister resigns   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Famid stolen painting probe 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An Italian junior culture minister has 
OL,6, resigned amid accusations of laundering
OL,7, stolen goods, which he denies.         
OL,9,FVittorio Sgarbi made the announcement  
OL,10,Fbefore beginning a lecture in Milan,   
OL,11,Fsaying he was quitting "to avoid a     
OL,12,Fconflict of interest".                 
OL,14,FProsecutors are investigating          
OL,15,Fallegations Mr Sgarbi, a renowned art  
OL,16,Fcritic, stole and modified a           
OL,17,F17th-Century painting.                 
OL,19,F"The Capture of Saint Peter" was       
OL,20,Freported stolen in 2013.               
